-Good.

5
00:01:05,982 --> 00:01:07,817
SUMMER OF 1995

6
00:01:07,901 --> 00:01:10,153
Gosh, don't they know
how to toss the ball around?

7
00:01:10,236 --> 00:01:11,613
I mean, come on.

8
00:01:11,946 --> 00:01:13,198
Forget it.

9
00:01:13,490 --> 00:01:15,450
What's the point of winning an event game?

10
00:01:15,533 --> 00:01:17,368
Our pitcher's shoulders can be spared.

11
00:01:17,452 --> 00:01:18,578
Right.

12
00:01:20,789 --> 00:01:22,665
Mom, let's clink our glasses.

13
00:01:27,128 --> 00:01:29,130
Jun, eat up. Isn't it great?

14
00:01:29,214 --> 00:01:31,132
-Eat as much as you want.
-Okay.

15
