16
00:01:34,594 --> 00:01:37,472
SAMJUNG DEPARTMENT STORE COLLAPSES
OVER 100 PEOPLE BURIED

17
00:01:37,555 --> 00:01:40,350
This is breaking news
from the scene of the accident.

18
00:01:40,767 --> 00:01:43,019
Constant sounds of sirens and screams

19
00:01:43,103 --> 00:01:45,063
are heard everywhere at the site.

20
00:01:45,438 --> 00:01:47,065
Everyone who managed to escape

21
00:01:47,148 --> 00:01:48,942
was covered in blood.

22
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:52,695
At the moment,
the official death toll reached 97,

23
00:01:52,821 --> 00:01:55,323
and the number of the injured reached 922.

24
00:01:55,615 --> 00:01:58,576
Here are the additional
victims who have been confirmed dead.

25
00:01:58,993 --> 00:02:01,621
Park Mi-jeong, Kim Cheol-su,

26
00:02:01,704 --> 00:02:04,457
Lee Myeong-hun, Yun Jae-jeong,
Kim Jung-bae, Song Eun-jeong,

27
