She just keeps sleeping.

201
00:13:04,492 --> 00:13:06,035
When we were here,

202
00:13:06,619 --> 00:13:07,536
we used to

203
00:13:08,412 --> 00:13:10,122
have yummy food together

204
00:13:10,831 --> 00:13:11,999
and chat, too.

205
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,376
It was nice.

206
00:13:17,588 --> 00:13:18,672
Ye-sol!

207
00:13:19,465 --> 00:13:21,217
Oh, Min-yong!

208
00:13:22,051 --> 00:13:23,093
There you are, Dr. Lee.

209
00:13:23,177 --> 00:13:25,262
I left some for you in your office.

210
00:13:25,513 --> 00:13:28,182
Try it before we serve it at dinner.

211
00:13:29,016 --> 00:13:30,184
It's Manila clam pancake.

212
00:13:30,267 --> 00:13:32,853
My mom is very good
at opening Manila clams.

213
00:13:33,771 --> 00:13:34,855
This is for you.

214
00:13:35,314 --> 00:13:37,107
Wow, it looks delicious.

215
00:13:37,691 --> 00:13:40,402
Does your mom work at the cafeteria now?

216
00:13:41,278 --> 00:13:43,155
No, she's just helping out.

217
00:13:43,572 --> 00:13:45,699
She has poor skills,
so she'll just open clams.

218
00:13:48,202 --> 00:13:51,080
She wants to thank the people here
for making Ji-yong happy.

219
00:13:55,084 --> 00:13:58,254
Dr. Lee, I think Ji-yong safely returned
to the planet he came from.

220
00:14:00,881 --> 00:14:01,882
This is so good.

221
00:14:03,217 --> 00:14:05,052
My mom saw him
in her dream last night.

222
00:14:05,135 --> 00:14:07,680
She said he looked very happy there,

223
00:14:08,222 --> 00:14:10,307
worrying about peace on Earth
sometimes, too.

224
00:14:16,355 --> 00:14:17,356
I'm glad to hear that.

225
00:14:17,606 --> 00:14:20,109
I thought he was lying
that he came from another planet,

226
00:14:21,235 --> 00:14:22,486
but I guess it was true.

